{
  "stem": "1415.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They marched us, and they-- they made sure that we all dressed properly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they took us to a photographer, and they had our picture taken.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I have a picture with our family in armbands, and I think my brother and my father were given jackets so that they looked presentable.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And-- because when they marched us out, they didn't give us time to do anything, just.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that picture ended up in my brother's hand in Litva, who, in turn, took it with him, and it survived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we all have copies of that picture.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then afterwards, we got into the bunker, and the first selection took place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] After the selection, my sisters went out to be selected, because they figured they were 16 and 18 at the time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And nobody's going to harm them, because they are strong, and they're young.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They're going to go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But they never returned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I was told by people that watched that selection that they were taken in-- in the right line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But by the end of the selection, they decided to take that whole group, and they ended up in Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Later on, we found out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So my sisters never returned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And when my sisters did not return, and we didn't know their fate at the time, my mother and my father, they were so-- my mother was so upset she just left the bunker, and so did most able bodies.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Except for us children and my grandmother and some people that didn't want to leave stayed on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We stayed until my brother saw fit to-- to get us out of there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
